Subject: The AD_ActivityCollection Job
Description: The customer needs assistance setting up the AD_ActivityCollection Job. The DC agent is currently monitored by NTP, and the log is being stored in NAM.
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c:
Launch the NAA console
Expand the Active Directory group
Expand 6.Activity
Expand the 0.Collection and select the AD_ActivityCollection
What_We_Know__c: The AD_ActivityCollection Job in the Netwrix Access Analyzer (Netwrix Enterprise Auditor) is not configured to collect data.
Next_Steps__c: Sending the information with the steps on how to configure the AD_ActivityCollection Job
Solution_Comment__c:
Step-by-step instructions on how to set up the AD_ActivityCollection Job in the Netwrix Access Analyzer/Enterprise Auditor.
